    mat(i_1; i_2) = -mat(d_11 d_12; d_21 d_22)^(-1) mat(c_11 c_12; c_21 c_22) mat(u_1; u_2) = mat(g_11 g_12; g_21 g_22) mat(u_1; u_2)
  $
